<br>
NES was a great system, and really changed the way we thought of the &quot;video game&quot;. SNES and Sega's Genesis added to the gaming industry, and expanded on what had been done on the NES. However I believe Playstation was ground breaking, and did for the 90s what NES did for the late 80s. It changed the face of console gaming. If I had to vote on best console of all time I would probably have to give the award to NES but it would be close.<br>
<br>
