8. Sonic the Hedgehog  Sega Genesis<br>
9. Final Fantasy 7 PSX<br>
10. Golden Axe      Sega Genesis<br>
<br>
11. Tomb Raider PSX<br>
12. Final Fantasy NES<br>
13. Mortal Combat Sega Genesis<br>
14. Ms. Pac Man Atari<br>
15. Asteroids  Atari<br>
<br>
